'''= "The school of commons is a growing network of local schools offering a modular series of workshops using tools for commoning".''' 

URL = https://schoolofcommons.be/

A initiative co-founded by Evi Swinnen, chair of the P2P Foundation and director of the Timelab artistic makerspace in Ghent, Belgium.


=Description=

"Over the last 4 years, Timelab has developed a School of Commons in Ghent, based on a deep analysis of commons practices. A multidisciplinary team created an open set of seven patterns - Dream, Practice, Identity, Organise, Impact, Resources and Context - to exchange knowledge and expertise about commoning and to start the transition to make your organisation, project or process more commons-based."
